{
  "texts": [
    "MEDITECH is collaborating with Google to leverage an LLM for drafting documentation notes that providers can edit before EHR incorporation.",
    "Similarly, Oracle Health's AI \"Clinical Digital Assistant\" uses digital information and patient-provider conversations to draft notes and propose follow-up actions.",
    "AI is expanding EHR data sources by incorporating new types of data acquired from treatment rooms equipped with ambient monitoring systems.",
    "For example, technologies like the OR Black Box can capture detailed point-of-care data, including video, audio, and patient physiology, which can be utilized by LLMs for enhanced healthcare analysis 31, 32.",
    "In research, informed consent is typically obtained from both patients and providers."
  ]
}